<DOCNO> AP880414-0053 </DOCNO>
<FILEID>AP-NR-04-14-88 0412EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>r p BC-SenateDelegates-List     04-14 0155</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-Senate Delegates-List,160</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>With PM-Super Delegates Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here is a list of the 32 senators nominated to
be delegates to the Democratic National Convention.
