become the parents of a daughter, Kathleen Alexandra Kennedy.
   The 7-pound, 9-ounce girl was born Wednesday at Northern
Westchester Hospital in Mount Kisco, N.Y., a spokeswoman in Sen.
Edward Kennedy's office said Thursday.
   The new baby is the 10th grandchild for Kennedy's mother, Ethel.
The new parents, both lawyers, also have a 3-year-old son, Robert
Kennedy III.
   The birth comes during the 20th anniversary of the late Robert
Kennedy's campaign for the presidency.
